highlights.description:
Featured Restaurant of the Month - 
YAMATO 
 
 Featured Restaurant of the Month - YAMATO 
 Yamato stands tall at the entrance of Westwood Village. Spanning two floors accommodating both casual and fine dining, Yamato offers fresh rolls, original Japanese sake and traditional bar items. Some of their famous specialty rolls include the crunchy roll, the baked lobster roll, the pink roll, and the BSCR.

highlights.description:
Featured Restaurant of the Month - Rubio's Fresh Mexican Grill 
 
 Featured Restaurant of the Month - Rubio's Fresh Mexican Grill 
 After first tasting a fish taco in San Felipe, Mexico, Ralph Rubio returned to San Diego to hand-craft his own recipe and introduced America to the fish taco.  Rubio's Fresh Mexican Grill's  famous fish tacos and many other freshly prepared Mexican dishes can be found at the Terrace Food Court in UCLA's Ackerman Union.
